CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1962, pg. A20 reads: "Salute - Mrs. Elvenia Yarborough (right) is shown presenting flowers to Mrs. W.C. Stallworth, as Mrs. Stallworth and her husband celebrated their 44th wedding anniversary. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Four women, one wearing dark satin hat and beaded necklace, and man, gathered at banquet table during the forty-fourth wedding anniversary of Mr. and Mrs. W. C. Stallworth in YMCA
